oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Chain Tie Downs
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Jeans, Roland S.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: link chain
milk fever
ketosis
mastitis
intravenous injection
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This is a four-foot piece of welded link chain. It has a grab hook on each end and it is used for a number of different purposes. The main purpose that I use it for is treating cows in tie stalls with milk fever, ketosis, mastitis, or any intravenous injection that I want to give.
